overview: Jayden really needs a massage, so she decides to take a chance and order in a male masseur.  Alexis is kind of a bitch and her best friend Melissa has had enough. So when asked to book Alexis's massage, Melissa has Kieran come over to seduce her instead.  Aleksa is in serious need of a massage. Lucky for her, bill is on the job. He'll make sure to put his hands in all the right places.  Brandi is outraged when her BFF sends over what seems to be a male prostitute for her birthday.  Holly is stressed. No matter what she does she can't seem to unwind. She even treats herself to a spa visit and she still can't relax.
tagline: The hottest pornstars getting the happiest of endings!
title: Dirty Masseur 2
